 d recognize our amazing graduates. This reception will be held on Friday\,
  May 22\, 2026\, starting at 4:30 pm. Words of recognition and awards will
  start at 5:30 pm. Refreshments and appetizers will be available for your 
 enjoyment.  \\nDetails: https://swatcentral.swarthmore.edu/?trumbaEmbed=v
